WEBVTT

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:24.359
♪The whole world is lit up♪

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:25.979
♪Because you exist♪

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:28.019
♪You're always♪

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:32.679
♪Somewhere close, flying with me♪

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.299
♪Go to where the wind blows♪

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.019
♪Hold tight♪

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:42.879
♪To the ray of light that belongs to us♪

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:47.929
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 7=

00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:49.929
I'll explain everything to you later.

00:00:49.930 --> 00:00:50.929
Right now,

00:00:50.930 --> 00:00:51.569
look into

00:00:51.570 --> 00:00:52.690
this for me.

00:00:52.930 --> 00:00:53.819
Boss,

00:00:53.820 --> 00:00:56.370
you're hiding behind so many layers
when you're with her.

00:00:56.780 --> 00:00:58.140
Don't you find it exhausting?

00:01:03.250 --> 00:01:04.340
You...

00:01:05.020 --> 00:01:05.819
This

00:01:05.820 --> 00:01:06.849
monitoring system

00:01:06.850 --> 00:01:07.819
needs an update.

00:01:07.820 --> 00:01:09.260
Other than that, there are no issues.

00:01:09.770 --> 00:01:10.620
Okay.

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:12.509
Sorry for the trouble, Captain Shen.

00:01:12.509 --> 00:01:13.689
(Shen Jibai)

00:01:13.690 --> 00:01:15.570
(is such a flirt.)

00:01:21.180 --> 00:01:22.860
You found my dad's attending physician?

00:01:23.610 --> 00:01:24.329
Good.

00:01:24.330 --> 00:01:25.450
I'm coming over now.

00:01:30.380 --> 00:01:32.640
(Medical Record Inspection Report)
I've seen my dad's attending doctor.

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:34.650
He said my dad
has obvious stroke symptoms.

00:01:34.970 --> 00:01:35.939
He can't speak

00:01:35.940 --> 00:01:36.980
or move.

00:01:37.460 --> 00:01:39.769
But even though the hospital
recommended observation,

00:01:39.770 --> 00:01:41.810
my dad suddenly checked himself out.

00:01:48.460 --> 00:01:49.980
I'll let you know if anything comes up.

00:01:50.050 --> 00:01:51.090
I'm hanging up.

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:55.099
Since leaving Hong's studio,

00:01:55.100 --> 00:01:56.980
you haven't said a single word to me.

00:01:57.130 --> 00:01:58.739
If you have a problem with me, Miss Mu,

00:01:58.740 --> 00:01:59.980
feel free to say it.

00:02:00.900 --> 00:02:02.730
How would I dare have a problem?

00:02:03.690 --> 00:02:05.689
I just want to remind you, Captain Shen,

00:02:05.690 --> 00:02:06.899
to behave yourself

00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:08.370
and stop flirting.

00:02:08.460 --> 00:02:10.300
It wouldn't be good if my stepmom

00:02:10.370 --> 00:02:11.530
found out about it.

00:02:11.610 --> 00:02:14.650
I only helped Miss Yan
look at the surveillance footage,

00:02:16.020 --> 00:02:17.489
and it was with your permission.

00:02:17.490 --> 00:02:19.019
You have exceptional skills,

00:02:19.020 --> 00:02:20.609
and your charm is irresistible.

00:02:20.610 --> 00:02:21.529
I respect that.

00:02:21.530 --> 00:02:22.580
Got a problem?

00:02:22.700 --> 00:02:23.740
Putting that aside,

00:02:24.770 --> 00:02:26.850
what do you think
about your dad's stroke?

00:02:27.860 --> 00:02:29.220
If he really had a stroke,

00:02:29.420 --> 00:02:31.810
he couldn't have appeared
in the exhibition video.

00:02:32.370 --> 00:02:33.900
The recovery time doesn't match up.

00:02:34.330 --> 00:02:35.580
What are you trying to say?

00:02:37.780 --> 00:02:39.329
There's something wrong
with my dad's video.

00:02:39.330 --> 00:02:40.769
(With such a severe stroke,)

00:02:40.770 --> 00:02:42.369
(how could he have recorded a video?)

00:02:42.370 --> 00:02:44.460
Towards a better future.

00:02:55.020 --> 00:02:56.090
(Jiang Hu.)

00:02:56.260 --> 00:02:57.460
(What is he doing here?)

00:03:00.210 --> 00:03:01.690
Shen Jibai, what are you doing?

00:03:01.740 --> 00:03:03.780
(We haven't settled our old scores yet.)

00:03:04.020 --> 00:03:06.620
(Mu Zhiyu will be in danger here.
We have to get out of here.)

00:03:11.260 --> 00:03:12.090
Hey.

00:03:12.300 --> 00:03:13.020
Hey!

00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:21.580
Hey!

00:03:22.740 --> 00:03:23.850
What are you doing?

00:03:24.370 --> 00:03:25.370
What's going on?

00:03:34.260 --> 00:03:34.970
Hey!

00:03:52.700 --> 00:03:53.489
Go first.

00:03:53.490 --> 00:03:55.060
I have some personal business to handle.

00:04:07.610 --> 00:04:09.810
(Shen Jibai is being so mysterious.)

00:04:10.210 --> 00:04:11.930
(I want to see what he's up to.)

00:04:39.530 --> 00:04:40.939
I finally found you,

00:04:40.940 --> 00:04:42.290
Shen Jibai.

00:04:42.700 --> 00:04:43.900
Who would've thought

00:04:44.090 --> 00:04:46.090
the boss of a security company

00:04:46.170 --> 00:04:47.820
would ever be caught alone?

00:04:57.940 --> 00:04:59.460
Why did you come back?

00:05:03.530 --> 00:05:04.379
I see.

00:05:04.380 --> 00:05:06.089
The security company boss

00:05:06.090 --> 00:05:07.969
went through all this trouble

00:05:07.970 --> 00:05:09.529
just to protect this little girl.

00:05:09.530 --> 00:05:10.820
(Security company?)

00:05:11.170 --> 00:05:12.490
(Boss?)

00:05:13.290 --> 00:05:14.050
Hey!

00:05:15.170 --> 00:05:16.290
It seems

00:05:16.530 --> 00:05:17.850
this little girl

00:05:18.260 --> 00:05:19.650
is very important to you.

00:05:21.700 --> 00:05:23.209
Then, don't blame me for being ruthless.

00:05:23.210 --> 00:05:24.380
Just try it.

00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:44.610
Shen Jibai,

00:05:44.900 --> 00:05:46.140
I'll be back.

00:05:47.210 --> 00:05:47.900
Next time,

00:05:47.940 --> 00:05:49.220
you won't be so lucky.

00:05:51.970 --> 00:05:53.970
The boss of Security Group...

00:05:54.290 --> 00:05:56.260
Let's have a good talk, shall we?

00:05:59.970 --> 00:06:00.970
So tell me,

00:06:01.500 --> 00:06:02.900
should I call you Captain Shen

00:06:02.970 --> 00:06:04.050
or President Shen?

00:06:04.620 --> 00:06:05.940
You should just call me Shen Jibai.

00:06:05.970 --> 00:06:06.619
After all,

00:06:06.620 --> 00:06:08.460
I'm still your
personal bodyguard right now.

00:06:09.410 --> 00:06:10.900
Personal bodyguard?

00:06:12.170 --> 00:06:14.619
As the boss
of the prominent Security Group,

00:06:14.620 --> 00:06:16.619
you still need
to be my personal bodyguard?

00:06:16.620 --> 00:06:18.290
Isn't that beneath you?

00:06:20.020 --> 00:06:20.900
Tell me,

00:06:21.260 --> 00:06:22.460
who was that man just now?

00:06:24.260 --> 00:06:25.290
His name is Jiang Hu.

00:06:25.770 --> 00:06:27.499
He belongs to an overseas gang

00:06:27.500 --> 00:06:28.650
and is my arch-rival.

00:06:35.460 --> 00:06:37.650
Since you have
your own security company,

00:06:38.060 --> 00:06:39.209
why did you come to Mu Group

00:06:39.210 --> 00:06:40.580
to be the Head of Security?

00:06:42.090 --> 00:06:43.530
What exactly is your goal?

00:06:47.730 --> 00:06:49.090
If I said

00:06:49.770 --> 00:06:51.340
I did it out of interest,

00:06:51.730 --> 00:06:52.780
would you believe me?

00:06:53.380 --> 00:06:54.410
I'd believe you.

00:06:56.060 --> 00:06:57.729
But I don't know
if my stepmom, Xu Mingzhu,

00:06:57.730 --> 00:06:58.940
would believe it.

00:07:02.620 --> 00:07:03.940
I came to the Mu family

00:07:03.970 --> 00:07:05.780
because of a transfer record.

00:07:05.900 --> 00:07:07.260
What transfer record?

00:07:09.530 --> 00:07:10.780
Three months ago,

00:07:11.730 --> 00:07:13.460
my mom passed away
after refusing treatment.

00:07:14.170 --> 00:07:15.089
Among her belongings

00:07:15.090 --> 00:07:16.970
was a transfer record from Mu Group.

00:07:17.770 --> 00:07:19.490
It clearly shows

00:07:19.850 --> 00:07:21.380
that since I was five,

00:07:22.850 --> 00:07:25.340
my mom had received
transfers from Mu Group.

00:07:26.970 --> 00:07:28.580
Also, when I was five,

00:07:29.290 --> 00:07:29.899
my mom

00:07:29.900 --> 00:07:31.490
moved me abroad,

00:07:32.090 --> 00:07:33.650
and we began a life of wandering.

00:07:33.770 --> 00:07:35.050
Are you saying

00:07:36.210 --> 00:07:37.409
someone inside Mu Group

00:07:37.410 --> 00:07:39.939
has been sending money
to you and your mom

00:07:39.940 --> 00:07:41.209
to support your lives?

00:07:41.210 --> 00:07:43.900
I want to find out
my connection to Mu Group.

00:07:43.940 --> 00:07:45.849
So that day
you went to the nursing home,

00:07:45.850 --> 00:07:48.260
you weren't working
for Xu Mingzhu either.

00:07:48.530 --> 00:07:50.410
Instead, your goal was the same as mine.

00:07:51.290 --> 00:07:52.780
You were looking for Mu Chenzhou.

00:07:53.090 --> 00:07:54.340
You could say that.

00:07:54.940 --> 00:07:55.940
However,

00:07:57.580 --> 00:07:59.649
it's impossible
that my dad sent you money.

00:07:59.650 --> 00:08:01.850
He's so biased
toward sons over daughters.

00:08:01.900 --> 00:08:03.940
If he knew he had a son out there,

00:08:04.410 --> 00:08:06.050
he would have brought him back long ago.

00:08:07.210 --> 00:08:08.460
One last question.

00:08:08.620 --> 00:08:09.970
Why did Xu Mingzhu

00:08:10.460 --> 00:08:12.380
have you watch me?

00:08:13.900 --> 00:08:15.020
What do you think?

00:08:15.210 --> 00:08:16.900
I advise you not to play tricks.

00:08:17.330 --> 00:08:18.490
I warned you,

00:08:18.900 --> 00:08:20.819
Xu Mingzhu is only interested in profit.

00:08:20.820 --> 00:08:22.490
She's capable of anything.

00:08:23.700 --> 00:08:24.649
Tell me,

00:08:24.650 --> 00:08:26.050
if she found out

00:08:26.700 --> 00:08:27.819
you were lying to her,

00:08:27.820 --> 00:08:29.140
what would happen to you?

00:08:29.330 --> 00:08:31.090
I don't know her specific goal,

00:08:31.650 --> 00:08:32.730
but I know

00:08:32.930 --> 00:08:35.010
she wants the password to a bank safe.

00:08:35.450 --> 00:08:37.490
As long as I
get close to you and get it,

00:08:37.810 --> 00:08:39.540
she'll give me a large sum of money.

00:08:40.020 --> 00:08:40.820
Fine.

00:08:41.930 --> 00:08:44.340
I'll check the truth of this myself.

00:08:44.810 --> 00:08:46.370
If you dare lie to me,

00:08:50.690 --> 00:08:52.010
you will be dead.

00:09:04.260 --> 00:09:05.340
(Grandpa...)

00:09:06.380 --> 00:09:07.300
(Mom...)

00:09:08.860 --> 00:09:11.010
(I miss you so much when I'm alone.)

00:09:12.570 --> 00:09:14.420
(If only you were still here.)

00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:20.120
(Luyao)

00:09:23.380 --> 00:09:24.340
How is it?

00:09:25.170 --> 00:09:26.019
Boss,

00:09:26.020 --> 00:09:26.649
I've checked.

00:09:26.650 --> 00:09:28.700
Regarding the overseas security company,

00:09:28.810 --> 00:09:31.540
Shen Jibai is indeed the president.

00:09:31.690 --> 00:09:34.090
He built the company from scratch.

00:09:34.260 --> 00:09:35.739
But he's very mysterious.

00:09:35.740 --> 00:09:37.099
The publicly announced founder

00:09:37.100 --> 00:09:38.660
is actually his stepfather.

00:09:39.140 --> 00:09:41.420
But he passed away many years ago.

00:09:41.860 --> 00:09:43.370
Fine, I understand.

00:09:44.340 --> 00:09:45.820
Thanks for the investigation.

00:09:46.050 --> 00:09:46.739
Please

00:09:46.740 --> 00:09:48.700
keep looking into Shen Jibai for me.

00:09:49.100 --> 00:09:49.979
Now,

00:09:49.980 --> 00:09:52.340
I've officially
started working at Mu Group.

00:09:52.450 --> 00:09:53.460
Next,

00:09:53.900 --> 00:09:56.130
you should come
work here as an assistant.

00:09:56.690 --> 00:09:57.580
Understood.

00:10:03.170 --> 00:10:05.730
(Should I go talk to Shen Jibai?)

00:10:15.020 --> 00:10:19.250
♪Light comes beaming in♪

00:10:19.390 --> 00:10:23.759
♪Landing on my skin♪

00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:28.250
♪Warms the space you left behind♪

00:10:32.470 --> 00:10:36.730
♪Shadows move around♪

00:10:36.820 --> 00:10:41.019
♪Awake, racing thoughts♪

00:10:41.020 --> 00:10:45.550
♪Try to keep the memories safe♪

00:10:49.150 --> 00:10:54.940
♪Don't slip away♪

00:10:57.390 --> 00:11:01.959
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:06.359
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:10.680
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:10.700 --> 00:11:14.680
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:15.150 --> 00:11:19.459
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:19.460 --> 00:11:23.789
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:23.790 --> 00:11:28.099
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪

00:11:28.100 --> 00:11:34.250
♪I'm all yours, all yours♪